  "body": {
    "export_view": {
      "value": "<p>RepairQ is a cloud-based system, so we are compatible with many brands of printers, barcode scanners, and other peripherals for your business setup. Our program works best in Chrome Brower, and we also support Microsoft Edge, Mozilla Firefox, and Safari browsers.</p><p>For a list of our recommended hardware, check out this link: <a class=\"external-link\" href=\"https://www.servicecentral.com/products/repair-q/hardware-recommendations/\" rel=\"nofollow\">RepairQ Hardware Recommendations</a>.</p><p>Our Support Team can assist with any RepairQ-related connectivity issues, however, there may be initial setup procedures for establishing a connection between your device(s) and your computer that are handled independently. Often, there are programs and drivers to install before your device(s) will properly work.</p><p>Below, we have provided a list of commonly-used devices with links to purchase these items and their support resources online.</p><span class=\"confluence-embedded-file-wrapper image-center-wrapper\"><img class=\"confluence-embedded-image image-center\" src=\"https://servicecentral.atlassian.net/wiki/download/attachments/1933869057/Control%20-%20f79824.png?api=v2\"></span><h2 id=\"RecommendedHardwareTroubleshootingResources-BarcodeScannerResources\">Barcode Scanner Resources</h2><p><a class=\"external-link\" href=\"https://www.amazon.com/Vcall-Omnidirectional-Automatic-Barcode-Hands-Free/dp/B015XXFQ5C/ref=as_li_ss_tl?s=electronics&amp;ie=UTF8&amp;qid=1508436100&amp;sr=1-4&amp;keywords=desktop+barcode+scanners&amp;th=1&amp;linkCode=sl1&amp;tag=repaiio-20&amp;linkId=db6e8126168ce590f2bf52b2d5d2599b\" rel=\"nofollow\"><strong>Vcall Barcode Scanner</strong></a> \u2014 <a class=\"external-link\" href=\"https://images-na.ssl-images-amazon.com/images/I/91R3Qt0pW-L.pdf\" rel=\"nofollow\">Vcall Barcode Scanner Support Page</a></p><p><a class=\"external-link\" href=\"https://www.amazon.com/CHS-Imager-Barcode-Scanner-Gray/dp/B007ZW3H6U/ref=as_li_ss_tl?s=electronics&amp;ie=UTF8&amp;qid=1510001780&amp;sr=1-1&amp;keywords=CHS+7Ci&amp;linkCode=sl1&amp;tag=repaiio-20&amp;linkId=0ba52f4c6ea3bd1083cc193ae23a864f\" rel=\"nofollow\"><strong>Socket Mobile Scanner</strong></a> \u2014\u00a0<a class=\"external-link\" href=\"https://www.socketmobile.com/support/downloads/series-7\" rel=\"nofollow\">Socket Mobile Scanner Support Page</a></p><p /><h2 id=\"RecommendedHardwareTroubleshootingResources-LabelPrinters\">Label Printers</h2><p>Installing the proper driver(s) for your printer will help <a href=\"https://servicecentral.atlassian.net/wiki/spaces/SCD/pages/1934229707/QZ+Integrated+Printing+-+Start+Here\" data-linked-resource-id=\"1934229707\" data-linked-resource-version=\"13\" data-linked-resource-type=\"page\">Integrated Printing</a> run smoothly.</p><p><a class=\"external-link\" href=\"https://www.amazon.com/Zebra-GK420d-Desktop-Thermal-Printer/dp/B01N1YAANZ/ref=as_li_ss_tl?s=electronics&amp;ie=UTF8&amp;qid=1510001843&amp;sr=1-3&amp;keywords=Zebra+GK420d&amp;linkCode=sl1&amp;tag=repaiio-20&amp;linkId=028f6f73c38dcbc3f6542cb4c2df323c\" rel=\"nofollow\"><strong>Zebra GK420d</strong></a><strong> </strong>\u2014\u00a0<a class=\"external-link\" href=\"https://www.zebra.com/us/en/support-downloads/printers/desktop/gk420d.html\" rel=\"nofollow\">Zebra GK420d Support Page</a></p><p><a class=\"external-link\" href=\"https://www.amazon.com/DYMO-LabelWriter-Thermal-Printer-1750283/dp/B0027JIIKQ/ref=as_li_ss_tl?s=electronics&amp;ie=UTF8&amp;qid=1510001866&amp;sr=1-1&amp;keywords=Dymo+LabelWriter+450&amp;linkCode=sl1&amp;tag=repaiio-20&amp;linkId=13f8e05642e9f3093a6ebe2903957dad\" rel=\"nofollow\"><strong>Dymo LabelWriter 450</strong></a> \u2014\u00a0<a class=\"external-link\" href=\"http://www.dymo.com/en-US/labelwriter-450-turbo-label-printer\" rel=\"nofollow\">Dymo LabelWriter 450 Support Page</a></p><p><a class=\"external-link\" href=\"https://www.amazon.com/Brother-QL-700-High-speed-Professional-Printer/dp/B005TJMC0S/ref=as_li_ss_tl?s=electronics&amp;ie=UTF8&amp;qid=1510001896&amp;sr=1-2&amp;keywords=Brother+QL-700&amp;linkCode=sl1&amp;tag=repaiio-20&amp;linkId=28c5db93454cac63047279a5610e1ff1\" rel=\"nofollow\"><strong>Brother QL-700</strong></a> \u2014\u00a0<a class=\"external-link\" href=\"https://support.brother.com/g/b/faqtop.aspx?c=as_ot&amp;lang=en&amp;prod=lpql700eas\" rel=\"nofollow\">Brother QL-700 Support Page</a></p><p /><h2 id=\"RecommendedHardwareTroubleshootingResources-ReceiptPrinters\">Receipt Printers</h2><p><a class=\"external-link\" href=\"https://www.amazon.com/Epson-TM-T88V-Thermal-Receipt-Printer/dp/B003JVT1AW/ref=as_li_ss_tl?s=electronics&amp;ie=UTF8&amp;qid=1510001953&amp;sr=1-3&amp;keywords=Epson+TM-T88V+Thermal+Receipt+Printer&amp;linkCode=sl1&amp;tag=repaiio-20&amp;linkId=7d55e80a800c0dc9d06ef534224bd528\" rel=\"nofollow\"><strong>Epson TM-T88V Receipt Printer</strong></a> \u2014\u00a0<a class=\"external-link\" href=\"https://epson.com/Support/Point-of-Sale/Thermal-Printers/Epson-TM-T88V/s/SPT_C31CA85011\" rel=\"nofollow\">Epson TM-T88V Receipt Printer Support Page</a></p><p><a class=\"external-link\" href=\"https://www.amazon.com/Star-MicronicsTSP143IIU-GRY-US-ECO/dp/B003NE43EY/ref=as_li_ss_tl?s=electronics&amp;ie=UTF8&amp;qid=1510002008&amp;sr=1-3&amp;keywords=Star+TSP100&amp;linkCode=sl1&amp;tag=repaiio-20&amp;linkId=454d6f41190adf86f82ab2c3be577162\" rel=\"nofollow\"><strong>Star TSP 100 Printer</strong></a><strong> </strong>\u2014\u00a0<a class=\"external-link\" href=\"https://starmicronics.com/pages/TSP100\" rel=\"nofollow\">Star TSP 100 Printer Support Page</a></p><p /><h2 id=\"RecommendedHardwareTroubleshootingResources-CashDrawer\">Cash Drawer</h2><p><a class=\"external-link\" href=\"https://www.amazon.com/APG-VB320-AW1616-Standard-Duty-MultiPRO-Interface/dp/B0156JJPX2/ref=as_li_ss_tl?s=electronics&amp;ie=UTF8&amp;qid=1510001930&amp;sr=1-2&amp;keywords=APG+Vasario&amp;linkCode=sl1&amp;tag=repaiio-20&amp;linkId=6cb8cbe9228c55985164a29e59b16538\" rel=\"nofollow\"><strong>APG Vasario Cash Drawer</strong></a> \u2014\u00a0<a class=\"external-link\" href=\"https://www.cashdrawer.com/tutorials/\" rel=\"nofollow\">APG Vasario Cash Drawer Support Page</a></p><p /><h2 id=\"RecommendedHardwareTroubleshootingResources-QpopCompanion(Tablets)\">Qpop Companion (Tablets)</h2><p><a href=\"https://servicecentral.atlassian.net/wiki/spaces/SCD/pages/1936523288/Qpop+Companion+System+Requirements\" data-linked-resource-id=\"1936523288\" data-linked-resource-version=\"8\" data-linked-resource-type=\"page\">Qpop\u2122 Companion System Requirements</a></p><p /><p /><p>START 1.18.X</p>",
